All he sent was a pair of scissors

5
00:00:10.266 --> 00:00:11.466
How is that possible?

6
00:00:11.900 --> 00:00:12.700
Lu Shanshan

7
00:00:13.266 --> 00:00:14.800
Is there anything else you want to say?

8
00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:17.566
Tarzan, what the hell is going on?

9
00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:20.966
Shut up! Don't you believe me?

10
00:00:22.466 --> 00:00:23.833
Of course I believe

11
00:00:24.666 --> 00:00:26.633
