13
00:00:28.366 --> 00:00:29.200
Oh.

14
00:00:29.966 --> 00:00:31.466
Then explain to me

15
00:00:31.733 --> 00:00:34.100
Why on your big day

16
00:00:34.266 --> 00:00:36.466
Your family will give you a pair of scissors.

17
00:00:36.600 --> 00:00:37.466
Yes, Shanshan

18
00:00:37.933 --> 00:00:39.466
Why is that?

19
00:00:40.100 --> 00:00:43.266
You are all too materialistic.

20
00:00:43.333 --> 00:00:44.433
Home gift

21
00:00:44.666 --> 00:00:46.566
Naturally have their own business

22
00:00:47.366 --> 00:00:50.066
Then tell me what kind of business is there?

23
00:00:50.666 --> 00:00:53.000
It's very simple, my Luo family

24
00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:55.866
I hope my husband will get rid of his worries about the past.

25
00:00:55.966 --> 00:00:57.833
Be good to me wholeheartedly

26
00:00:58.666 --> 00:01:01.466
Yeah, there's nothing wrong with that explanation

27
00:01:01.466 --> 00:01:02.600
It does make sense.

28
00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:03.766
It turned out to be so

29
00:01:03.966 --> 00:01:05.600
Shanshan, sorry.

30
00:01:05.700 --> 00:01:07.433
I almost suspected you just now

31
00:01:08.100 --> 00:01:10.100
Husband, I don't blame you.

32
00:01:10.133 --> 00:01:12.166
Blame this stinky village girl for making trouble

33
00:01:12.166 --> 00:01:13.666
Also provoke our relationship

34
00:01:17.700 --> 00:01:20.166
Wonderful I have to say

35
00:01:20.166 --> 00:01:21.666
As a liar

